WEBVTT



00:00:11.008 --> 00:00:14.464
I'm Derek Walker. I'm the pastor of the Oxford Bible Church today.

00:00:14.144 --> 00:00:17.728
And I'm excited today to introduce you to my book,

00:00:17.408 --> 00:00:20.960
Mount Moriah, Golgotha and the garden tomb.

00:00:21.568 --> 00:00:24.736
The central events of history are the death,

00:00:24.480 --> 00:00:27.872
Burial and resurrection of Jesus Christ.

00:00:27.904 --> 00:00:29.024
This book.

00:00:29.024 --> 00:00:37.280
is filled with diagrams and photographs from Jerusalem and it reveals exactly where these momentous events took place.

00:00:37.440 --> 00:00:47.488
The Bible will come to life as you see in detail how the drama of redemption was acted out on Mount Moriah in perfect fulfillment of prophecy.

00:00:47.008 --> 00:00:47.840
Prophecy.

00:00:49.216 --> 00:00:50.656
The book starts.

00:00:50.624 --> 00:00:55.456
with the amazing events of Genesis 22 when Abraham offers up

00:00:55.328 --> 00:00:57.088
His son, Isaac.

00:00:56.992 --> 00:00:58.464
On Mount Moriah.

00:00:58.304 --> 00:00:59.616
God chose that.

00:00:59.776 --> 00:01:02.304
As a the special place because

00:01:03.200 --> 00:01:05.024
Two thousand years later,

00:01:04.864 --> 00:01:06.496
He would offer up.

00:01:06.464 --> 00:01:08.480
His own beloved son.

00:01:08.320 --> 00:01:09.952
Jesus Christ.

00:01:10.272 --> 00:01:16.096
on the very same location. And in Genesis 22 we make an in-depth study of how

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:17.728
It was prophesied

00:01:17.888 --> 00:01:18.816
That

00:01:18.656 --> 00:01:25.312
in that same place God would give his son as the final sacrifice and that enables us

00:01:25.088 --> 00:01:31.648
to work out where Jesus was crucified. We've put it together with the evidence in the New Testament.

00:01:31.680 --> 00:01:36.352
As to where he was crucified, where he was buried, and where he rose from the dead.

00:01:36.288 --> 00:01:44.288
And we are able to prove that the garden tomb is indeed the place of Christ's burial and resurrection.

00:01:44.736 --> 00:01:53.440
We also will harmonize the different gospel accounts to show the events of that day and help them come to life for you.

00:01:53.216 --> 00:02:03.264
And I believe you will find this an exciting read. And along with this book, we also have made some two DVD documentaries, Mount Moriah and Golgotha.

00:02:02.784 --> 00:02:09.024
in Golgotha and Golgotha in the garden tomb that will further inspire you.

00:02:08.768 --> 00:02:14.080
In this study and what could be more important than to see

00:02:14.112 --> 00:02:16.288
The events.

00:02:16.352 --> 00:02:17.344
Of

00:02:17.152 --> 00:02:18.688
Good christ

00:02:18.432 --> 00:02:20.608
Death and resurrection.

00:02:20.576 --> 00:02:22.208
I believe this will

00:02:22.048 --> 00:02:26.912
strengthen you greatly in your faith. So I recommend you get this book.

00:02:27.296 --> 00:02:29.440
Mount Moriah, go gothir.

00:02:29.184 --> 00:02:30.688
And the garden, too.
